08:41.103 --> 08:43.981
I wanted the opportunity
to decline directly.

08:48.361 --> 08:49.737
Heathen.

08:49.820 --> 08:51.364
Feel like feeding your spirit?

08:55.034 --> 08:57.828
-My spirit could eat. [chuckles]
-[Kordell] Excellent.

09:01.541 --> 09:04.877
[Kordell] Here's a passage
that I think, Reggie,

09:04.961 --> 09:07.922
you especially will appreciate.

09:08.548 --> 09:10.258
Matthew 5:39.

09:10.341 --> 09:13.553
"But I tell you not
to resist an evil person,

09:13.636 --> 09:15.846
but whoever slaps you on your right cheek,

09:15.930 --> 09:18.474
turn the other to him also."

09:18.558 --> 09:19.850
Runnin' out of cheeks.

09:19.934 --> 09:20.977
I'm sorry, what was that?

09:21.060 --> 09:23.229
I love Jesus.

09:23.312 --> 09:25.314
Um, how about this one?

09:25.398 --> 09:29.610
"If you bring forth what is within you,
what you bring forth will save you.

09:29.694 --> 09:31.988
If you do not bring forth
what is within you,

09:32.071 --> 09:34.532
what you do not bring forth
will destroy you."

09:35.283 --> 09:37.326
Uh, where did Jesus say that?

09:37.410 --> 09:39.870
Gospel of Thomas.
It's apocryphal, but it goes in.

09:39.954 --> 09:42.206
[clearing throat]
You know what? We should pray.

09:50.590 --> 09:52.341
[sighs] Dear Heavenly Father,

09:52.425 --> 09:55.928
I ask that you open Reggie's heart
to forgive his enemies.

09:56.012 --> 10:00.558
Guide him to let go and let God lead him.

10:00.975 --> 10:02.435
You know what? This is a lot.

10:02.518 --> 10:06.355
If you want to go, leave before he starts
listing adjectives about Jesus.

10:06.439 --> 10:08.566
[Kordell] Let your light shine through

10:08.649 --> 10:11.527
to the path of your son, Jesus,

10:11.611 --> 10:13.946
who is both gracious and merciful,

10:14.030 --> 10:16.324
rageful but fair,

10:16.407 --> 10:21.454
glorious but humble, sweet but savory...

10:23.956 --> 10:25.583
-Hey.
-Hey.

10:26.667 --> 10:28.878
Don't tell me you're moving into A-P.

10:28.961 --> 10:31.756
No, no, I'm, uh--I was gonna meet, um...

10:33.090 --> 10:34.800
Hey, did you think maybe
a little bit more

10:34.884 --> 10:37.428
about us, you know, sittin' down or...

10:38.054 --> 10:42.350
Gabe, I really don't need
or want to talk right now.

10:42.433 --> 10:43.893
Yeah.

10:50.316 --> 10:52.818
-Well, if you change your mind...
-Hmm.

11:04.872 --> 11:06.207
[exhales]

11:13.798 --> 11:16.592
-[Reggie] You two get a room.
-[man] We already got one. You jealous?

11:16.675 --> 11:18.511
Actually, yeah.

11:18.594 --> 11:20.596
You know they got all the rest
of us Negroes doubling up

11:20.679 --> 11:22.598
