11:22.681 --> 11:23.891
[chuckling]

11:23.974 --> 11:25.017
Hey.

11:28.270 --> 11:31.857
What you did at Town Hall was... so brave.

11:31.941 --> 11:34.193
You really stuck it to the man.

11:34.276 --> 11:35.528
[chuckles]

11:35.611 --> 11:38.239
Well, I'm, uh... I'm a great sticker.

11:38.322 --> 11:40.825
[laughs] I'll bet.

11:41.492 --> 11:42.618
Text me later.

11:46.580 --> 11:48.249
Man, this shit's too easy.

11:48.332 --> 11:49.667
Am I right?

11:49.750 --> 11:50.835
Right about what?

11:51.627 --> 11:52.753
Man, come on.

11:52.837 --> 11:55.840
The silver lining to all
of this is the sympathy pussy.

11:55.923 --> 11:58.092
I mean, you gotta be swimming in it, bro.

11:58.175 --> 12:01.011
The fuck are you talking about, man?

12:02.179 --> 12:04.432
Dude, look,
ever since I broke that window,

12:04.515 --> 12:06.517
I've logged around a quarter-mile of ass.

12:06.600 --> 12:08.561
Reparations never felt so good.

12:08.644 --> 12:11.313
[laughs]

12:11.397 --> 12:12.982
That was your takeaway?

12:13.065 --> 12:15.401
[laughing]

12:17.027 --> 12:19.071
You want to get fucked up like old times?

12:19.155 --> 12:20.239
Fuck yeah.

12:20.322 --> 12:23.701
♪ I finally found... ♪

12:23.784 --> 12:27.329
