12:47.516 --> 12:49.477
This would be a good bit
for the magazine, though.

12:49.560 --> 12:50.686
-Pass.
-[Kurt] Oh, come on.

12:50.769 --> 12:51.604
It's gonna be awesome.

12:51.687 --> 12:53.731
