13:30.059 --> 13:33.312
How you boys feel about a little
Maryland-Massachusetts, huh?

13:35.272 --> 13:37.691
MDMA?

13:37.775 --> 13:39.944
-[laughing]
-Ah, there it is.

13:40.027 --> 13:42.363
-That was solid.
-Reg, what do you say?

13:43.113 --> 13:45.074
-Fuck it.
-[laughs]

13:45.157 --> 13:47.159
Man... Thank you.

13:47.243 --> 13:49.578
