13:57.670 --> 13:59.463
makes me like you even less.

14:00.130 --> 14:03.259
You  Pastiche  cats, man,
y'all talk down to us

14:03.342 --> 14:05.553
like we intellectual lightweights.

14:05.636 --> 14:08.264
