14:08.347 --> 14:10.975
Nigga, it's supposed to be aimed
at the powerful,

14:11.058 --> 14:14.979
and y'all just...
trying to get a reaction.

14:15.062 --> 14:16.438
You're not wrong.

14:18.190 --> 14:20.025
This must be some strong shit.

14:21.151 --> 14:22.486
