15:27.968 --> 15:28.969
[both laugh]

15:29.053 --> 15:31.472
He even quoted Jay-Z. He said...

15:31.555 --> 15:33.015
[as Dean Fairbanks] "You got 99 problems,

15:33.098 --> 15:34.725
but your head shouldn't be one of them."

15:34.808 --> 15:35.643
[Reggie laughs]

15:35.726 --> 15:38.771
I told him
to never say that corny shit again.

15:39.438 --> 15:41.982
Parents. You raise 'em the best you can.

15:42.066 --> 15:44.026
They always trying to act grown.

15:44.109 --> 15:45.235
Mm.

15:47.154 --> 15:49.573
Shit, I still ain't even told my dad yet.

15:52.368 --> 15:53.661
Why not?

15:53.744 --> 15:56.538
A million reasons, man.

15:56.622 --> 15:59.416
Like, how you tell a former Black Panther

15:59.500 --> 16:01.418
that you got punked by a rent-a-cop?

16:02.127 --> 16:03.545
At least you broke a window.

16:03.629 --> 16:05.839
Shit, all I got was a white roommate.

16:06.799 --> 16:08.300
A really white roommate.

16:08.384 --> 16:10.052
[laughs]

16:10.135 --> 16:11.553
You use a washcloth, right?

16:12.638 --> 16:14.390
Nah, nigga, I use a pouf.

