right now, man.

16:28.487 --> 16:31.281
I mean, I got my
"building a more inclusive world

16:31.365 --> 16:34.827
through the technologies we use"
thing, and, you know...

16:36.537 --> 16:38.539
What do you have?

16:41.750 --> 16:44.128
Bro. Troy.

16:45.337 --> 16:46.630
You all right, my dude?

16:48.841 --> 16:50.384
